Title: NxtIRF mock genome containing human genes: SRSF1, SRSF2, SRSF3, TRA2A, TRA2B, TP53 and NSUN5
Description: Sequences from genes ( SRSF1, SRSF2, SRSF3, TRA2A, TRA2B, TP53 and NSUN5 ) were pasted together to create an artificial 'chrZ' chromosome. Chromosomal coordinates for gene annotations were modified accordingly.

Title: NxtIRF mock gene annotations containing human genes: SRSF1, SRSF2, SRSF3, TRA2A, TRA2B, TP53 and NSUN5
Description: Sequences from genes ( SRSF1, SRSF2, SRSF3, TRA2A, TRA2B, TP53 and NSUN5 ) were pasted together to create an artificial 'chrZ' chromosome. Chromosomal coordinates for gene annotations were modified accordingly.

Title: RNA-seq reads aligned to the NxtIRF mock genome from 02H003 of the Leucegene dataset (GSE67039)
Description: 02H003 - aligned reads (from this sample in GSE67039) were filtered by those mapping to genes in the NxtIRF mock genome. These were re-aligned to the mock genome using STAR.

Title: Mappability Exclusion Regions for Ensembl GRCh38 (hg38) release-94
Description: Ensembl GRCh38 (hg38) release-94 mappability exclusion regions were generated by NxtIRF, using a modification of the method as described in https://github.com/williamritchie/IRFinder/blob/master/bin/util/Mapability
